â€¢ Renamed framework to Î£â€‘Gravity and migrated notation to Î£â€‘based kernel for clusters.  
â€¢ Fixed Newtonianâ€‘limit, unit, and clumpingâ€‘sign bugs; unified f_gas normalization.  
â€¢ Replaced spherical 3â€‘D shell kernel by projected 2â€‘D Î£â€‘kernel for lensing to preserve triaxial geometry.  
â€¢ Validated geometry: removing local 1/(q_plane q_LOS) factor and using global normalization restores ~60% Î£â€‘sensitivity and ~20â€“30% Î¸_E lever arm.  
â€¢ Hierarchical calibration (Tierâ€‘1 clean) now yields Î¼_A = 16.47 Â± 0.58, Ïƒ_Aâ‰ˆ0.81, Ï‡Â²/d.o.f. = 2.21.  
â€¢ Blind holdâ€‘outs (A1689, MACS1149) revealed a trainingâ€‘set mass bias; roadmap below.

