- Clusters â€” Promising: Baryon-only Î£-kernel with triaxial projection fits MACS0416; hierarchical runs show Î¼_Aâ‰ˆ16.5, Ïƒ_A small; need mass-scaling and full systematics for population.

Referee objections and remedies (condensed):
- â€œWhere is the theory?â€ Provide stationary-phase derivation to Î£-kernel; conservative potential; PPN/GW statements (static sector only).
- â€œCosmology?â€ Provide K(k) pilot for shear 2-pt; scope as astrophysical effective theory v1.
- â€œBullet/offsets?â€ Add temperature/entropy gate (decohere shocked ICM); two-component mergers.
- â€œEllipticals?â€ Apply projected Î£-kernel to SÃ©rsic/Hernquist ellipsoids; mild pressure gate.
- â€œOverfitting?â€ Keep small global set {A_c, â„“0â‹†, Î³, p, n_coh}; per-cluster geometry nuisance; report Î”BIC/AIC.
- â€œRedshift/Î£_crit/source z?â€ Use Î£_crit(z_l,z_s) exactly; integrate over p(z_s) when available; propagate in hierarchy.

Population mass-scaling plan (this work):
- Model: â„“0(M) = â„“0,â‹† (R500/1 Mpc)^Î³; compare Î³=0 vs free Î³ by Î”BIC (decision: |Î”BIC|â‰¥6 decisive).
- Sample: Tier 1+2 CLASH, Nâ‰ˆ18 (exclude MACS0717); hold-outs A1689, MACS1149.
- Systematics to include: exact Î£_crit(z_l,z_s), source-z distributions or effective DLS/DS; per-cluster M200â†’M500 via c200; triaxial (q_LOS,q_plane) sampling; Îº_ext~N(0,0.03Â²) with correlation check; BCG mass component.
- Validation: posterior predictive checks (Ï‡Â²/d.o.f., residual patterns), blind hold-outs, and geometry correlations.

Execution checklist (repo scripts):
- Î³=0 baseline (fixed â„“0=200): scripts/run_hierarchical_tier12_mcmc.py --tiers 1,2 --exclude MACS0717 --outdir ...
- Î³ free (mass-scaling): scripts/run_mass_scaled_emcee.py --tiers 1,2 --exclude MACS0717 --outdir ...
