### Notes on nomenclature

To avoid confusion with prior drafts (â€œGeometryâ€‘Gated Manyâ€‘Path Gravityâ€), we standardize on Î£â€‘Gravity (Sigmaâ€‘Gravity) for the projectedâ€‘kernel formulation and retain pathâ€‘spectrum kernel for the galaxy stationaryâ€‘phase model.

